title: "SDK authoring DX polish: manifest-drift guard in scaffold tests, expectation key naming, repeated --capability, define* index signatures"
description: "Bundle of P3 SDK DX findings from the 2026-07-02 audit (Lane B, pm-6vy7): (1) generated scaffold test should call assertExtensionManifestMatchesBlueprint so manifest.json drift fails the starter suite; (2) test-expectation key drift across helpers (command/itemType/field/targetCommand/provider) is inconsistent; (3) repeated --capability flags silently last-win instead of erroring or composing; (4) [key: string]: unknown index signatures on define* option types weaken excess-property checking."
